The paper combines neural networks with formal reasoning to generate correct programs from specifications, which is a problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The focus on loop invariants suggests a connection to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the use of formal methods and logical specifications suggests a connection to logic (cs.LO).
